            <title>[LU-11224] T10PI assume several kernel features are enabled.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11224</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While porting to Power8 I ran into the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;obdclass: Unknown symbol ip_compute_csum (err 0)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is due to the new lustre T10Pi code assuming this is available. The same problem exist due to it assuming CONFIG_BLK_DEV_INTEGRITY is set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Power8 running 4.14 kernel. Can be any kernel with options assumed to be turned on.</environment>
